rComments: Laura is the nicest teacher. She knows the material very well. She comes to class well-prepared and lets us out early fairly often. Attendance isn't mandatory but you should go because you need the notes for the exam. I actually posted up a lot of my CMN 260 notes on GradeGuru.com. It's a free website so just sign up and look me up (ESKIM5).

she knows what she's talking about, and it's easy to understand all the topics in class. go to lecture/discussion and you'll be fine. plus, you get to chose how you want your grade weighted, and there's onle one optional paper, VERY interesting class, i highly recommend it
